{"article_id":"ibbXhFJgjhiisBOH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"The world got its first glimpse on Sunday into the investigation","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that has cast a cloud over Donald Trump 's presidency .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"After two days reading through Special Counsel Robert Mueller 's confidential report ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Attorney General William Barr sent a letter to Congress","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"offering a summary of the investigation into Russian interference in the 2016 presidential election and possible links to Trump 's campaign .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"In Barr 's letter , he said","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that no proof was found","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that the Trump campaign conspired with Russia","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"but said","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"no decision was made over whether the president obstructed justice .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Barr said","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that Mueller 's office left that charging decision to him and the Justice Department .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"`` The Special Counsel states","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"'while this report does not conclude","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"that the President committed a crime ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"it also does not exonerate him , ' ''","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"the letter states ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"quoting from the special counsel investigation .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Barr added","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that after review , he and Deputy Attorney General Rob Rosenstein `` have concluded","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that the evidence","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"developed during the Special Counsel 's investigation","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"is not sufficient","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"to establish","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that the President committed an obstruction-of-justice offense . ''","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Trump reacted to the news on Twitter","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"as he prepared to leave Mar-a-Lago , his private resort in Palm Beach , Fla. ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"writing","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"`` No Collusion , No Obstruction , Complete and Total EXONERATION .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"KEEP AMERICA GREAT ! ''","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"But Barr 's letter and his summary of the Mueller probe is really just the beginning ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"with lawmakers already pushing for the complete release of the investigation and underlying evidence .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Here 's what we know ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"what we do n't know ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"and what we might never find out :","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Mueller report :","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Special counsel Robert Mueller delivers report","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"marking end of investigation into Trump 's campaign , Russia","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Mueller report :","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Read Attorney General Barr 's letter to Congress","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"announcing end of Mueller 's Russia probe","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"`` The Special Counsel 's investigation did not find","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"that the Trump campaign or anyone","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"associated with it","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"conspired or coordinated with Russia in its efforts","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"to influence the 2016 U.S. presidential election , ''","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"Barr wrote in a letter to Congress","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"summarizing Mueller 's investigation .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"Barr noted","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"that this came `` despite multiple offers from Russian-affiliated individuals","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"to assist the Trump campaign . '' This was seen as a win for the president ,","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"who for years has railed against the investigation","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"and repeatedly said","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"there was no collusion with Russia .","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"`` It was just announced that there was no collusion with Russia , the most ridiculous thing","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"I 've ever heard .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"There was no collusion , folk , ''","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"Trump said","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"as he boarded Air Force One on the way back to Washington .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"After years investigating ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Mueller did n't say yes or no .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Instead , he offered the evidence","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"he had to Barr .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Mueller `` did not grat a conclusion","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"- one way or the other -","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"as to whether the examined conduct constituted obstruction , ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Barr notes in his letter to Congress .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"He noted","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Mueller 's office laid out evidence `` on both sides '' of the question","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"as to whether Trump committed a crime .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"`` The Special Counsel states","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"'while this report does not conclude","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"that the President committed a crime ,","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"it also does not exonerate him , ' ''","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Barr wrote ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"quoting from Mueller 's investigation .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Barr said","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"after examining the investigation , departmental policies","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"and talking with Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"he decided","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"there was not enough proof","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"that Trump committed a crime .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"`` I have concluded","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that the evidence","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"developed during the Special Counsel 's investigation","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"is not sufficient","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"to establish","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that the President committed an obstruction-of-justice offense , ''","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"Barr wrote .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"This letter tees up a massive push","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"to have the entirety of the report released to the public .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Democrats have been very vocal","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"in pushing for everything ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"including the underlying evidence ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"to be released .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"After Barr 's letter , House Judiciary Committee Chairman Jerry Nadler , D-N.Y. , said","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"he would be calling Barr to testify before the committee in coming days .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Barr 's letter was just a written summary of Mueller 's findings","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"- essentially parts of the report","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"Barr believes","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"he can share in accordance with Justice Department rules .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"The only information","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"Barr is required to reveal","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"is whether Mueller 's bosses overruled his investigative actions .","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"And Barr said","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"that did not happen .","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"We do n't know .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"The Justice Department said","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"it was `` comprehensive , ''","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"but did n't elaborate .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"A security officer from Mueller 's office delivered a printed copy to the offices of Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"who turned it over to Barr on Friday afternoon .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"What 's certain is that there will be a fight in Congress","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"to make the report public .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Lawmakers and Trump have indicated","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that they want the report to become public .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"But it 's unclear if that will stand","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"after the nation found out","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Mueller could not determine","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"whether the president committed a crime .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi said in a conference call with Democrats on Saturday","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"that she would reject any classified briefings of congressional intelligence leaders ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"known as the `` Gang of Eight . ''","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Any briefings ,","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"she said ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"should be unclassified","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"so the American public can be informed ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"according to an official","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"who was on the call .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Barr told lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that he was `` committed to as much transparency","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"as possible . ''","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"But he did not say","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"he would release Mueller 's complete report .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Instead , he said","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"he would consult with Mueller and Rosenstein","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"to `` determine what other information from the report can be released","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"consistent with the law ... and the Department 's long-standing practices and policies . ''","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"Barr has said","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that the department often can not reveal information about grand juries , or `` derogatory '' information about people","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"who have not been charged with a crime .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Peter Carr , Mueller 's spokesman , said","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"the special counsel would be `` concluding his service in the coming days . ''","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"A small staff would remain","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"to close down Mueller 's office .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"The office had already confirmed","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"that some of his prosecutors and investigators were leaving for other jobs .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"The investigation has led to charges against some of Trump 's closest advisers .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"And we know","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"what investigators believe","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"the 13 Russian nationals and a Russian troll farm did","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"to disrupt U.S. politics","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"and tilt the presidential election in Trump 's favor .","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"It 's still unclear whether Mueller 's report will speak to a pattern among those cases .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"`` That 's part of what the Mueller report is for .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"One of the things","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"the Mueller report will do","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"is it will attempt to put all of the indictments","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"Mueller has brought","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"into an overall context , ''","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"said Patrick Cotter , a white-collar defense attorney and a former federal prosecutor .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"In hundreds of pages of court filings , Mueller 's office revealed an extensive Russian intelligence operation","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"that used hacking , stolen documents and phony social media campaigns","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"to sow discord in U.S. politics","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"and support Trump 's campaign for the presidency .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"It revealed","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"that some of Trump 's aides worked eagerly","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"to benefit from that operation ,","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"seeking damaging information from Russians","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"even as Trump was seeking out business in the country .","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"And it revealed","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"that many of Trump 's aides then lied to Congress , federal investigators and the public","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"to downplay those connections .","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"Trump 's eldest son , Donald Trump Jr. , and his son-in-law , Jared Kushner , for example .","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"They , along with Manafort , met on June 9 , 2016 at Trump Tower with Russian attorney Natalia Veselnitskaya and several other Russians .","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"The meeting occurred","depth":16},{"id":180,"text":"after Trump Jr. was promised it would yield dirt on Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton .","depth":16},{"id":181,"text":"That meeting was a focal point of Mueller 's investigation ,","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"but the fact","depth":16},{"id":183,"text":"that no one has faced charges for it","depth":16},{"id":184,"text":"suggests","depth":15},{"id":185,"text":"Mueller 's team did n't think","depth":15},{"id":186,"text":"it amounted to a crime .","depth":15},{"id":187,"text":"The special counsel 's investigation revealed an extensive pattern of perjury .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"Several of Trump 's former advisers ,","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"including Flynn , Cohen and Stone ,","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"either admitted to","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"or were accused of lying .","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"Will Mueller address that in his report ?","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"Cotter hopes so .","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"`` Because to a federal prosecutor , I think","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"that it is a strikingly unusual aspect on this whole case .","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"That so many people lied to investigators , ''","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"Cotter said .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"Mueller referred his investigation on Cohen 's criminal activities to federal prosecutors in the Southern District of New York ,","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"who opened an inquiry into illegal hush-money payments","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"to silence two women","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"who claimed to have had sex with Trump .","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"Justice Department investigators have also been examining lobbying firms","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"tied to Manafort , and Trump 's inaugural committee .","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"The department has n't said","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"whether Mueller 's office made any other referrals .","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"Contributing : Kevin Johnson , Christal Hayes , Eliza Collins and Bart Jansen","depth":2},{"id":207,"text":"Your guide on what to expect from Robert Mueller 's final report on Trump , Russia investigations","depth":3},{"id":208,"text":"Robert Mueller has spent two years investigating Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":209,"text":"and he has n't said a word .","depth":6},{"id":210,"text":"It 's possible he never will .","depth":6},{"id":211,"text":"Manafort 's bad day underscores the peril in sprawling Trump probes ,","depth":5},{"id":212,"text":"some beyond the president 's control","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":425,"left":418,"right":424,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":418,"left":0,"right":417,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":417,"left":243,"right":416,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":238,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":217,"right":